ut from the tip of its tail. Over 5,000 different marks left by this Pok\u00e9mon have been found.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:black", "text": "It marks its territory by using its tail like a paintbrush. There are more than 5,000 different marks.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:black-2", "text": "It marks its territory by using its tail like a paintbrush. There are more than 5,000 different marks.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:crystal", "text": "The color of the mysterious fluid secreted from its tail is predeter\u00ad mined for each SMEARGLE.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:diamond", "text": "It marks its territory by using its tail like a paintbrush. There are more than 5,000 different marks.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:emerald", "text": "A SMEARGLE marks its territory using a fluid that leaks out from the tip of its tail. About 5,000 different marks left by this POK\u00e9MON have been found.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:firered", "text": "Once it becomes an adult, it has a tendency to let its comrades plant footprints on its back.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:gold", "text": "A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. It paints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:heartgold", "text": "A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. It paints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:leafgreen", "text": "A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. It paints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:moon", "text": "It draws symbols all over the place to mark its territory. In towns with many Smeargle, the walls are covered in graffiti.", "language": "en"}, {"gameVersionId": "game:omega-ruby", "text": "Smeargle marks the boundaries of its territory using a body fluid that leaks out from the tip of its tail. Ov